text: He yusupha! He agadi sacce yusupha! Tumhi amhala ya svapnaca khulasa sanga ki sata dhastapusta gayi aheta, jyanna sata dubalya gayi khata aheta ani sata agadi hiravi kanase aheta ani dusari sata kanase agadi sukaleli aheta. Yasathi ki mi parata ja'una tya lokanna sangave ki tya sarvanni januna ghyave
